short-description: This items is either referred to as the Hood Cowl Cover or Windshield Cowl Cover. It is the black plastic cover at the base of the windshield. There is a rubber seal that runs along the top edge that helps direct water down and away from the firewall. But because the rubber is exposed to sunlight it becomes dry and cracks with age. And that can allow water down into the various compartments and cavities in the firewall where rust will form.   The Cowl Cover also fades which makes it stand out in an otherwise detailed engine bay. Replacing it will give your engine compartment a fresh and cared for appearance. The marginal cost of the part goes a long way in sprucing up the engine bay. To finish off the restoration, add the "push button" mounting screws, new windshield wiper caps (wipers have to be removed to replace the Cowl Cover), and new clamps and grommets.   This item is one piece that covers the whole top of the firewall. Replacement is easy and straightforward but the wipers must be removed from the linkage. cleanDesc: No Holes License Plate Bracket - Premium Car Specific - E90/E92 325i...
short-description: There are universal license plate brackets and then there are car-specific license plate brackets. This E90/E92 no holes license plate bracket is form fitted to match the contours and opening in the 325i, 328i, 330i, and 335i front bumper. Unlike universal brackets, this will put the front license plate out of the way of critical air openings for the intercooler, radiator, or brake duct. It's also angled to follow the lines of the stock bumper - not stick out at a funny offset. It's the little details that take a good idea and make it great.   This bracket installs through the factory front tow hook point. It's made from high-strength cold-rolled steel and powdercoated for a long-lasting finish. PIAA Super Silicone Wiper Blade - 20 inch
short-description: Made of silicone rubber, PIAA wiper blades ensure greater visibility by coating the windshield with silicone to promote continuous water beading in inclement weather. Water beads up into droplets at low speeds that are easily removed by ordinary wiping. And at higher speeds, wind pressure pushes the water off the windshield, often without even requiring wiper use.     Each wiper insert is impregnated with a silicone agent, which automatically applies itself to the windshield as you wipe. The more you wipe, the better the "beading" effect of water droplets, causing droplets to simlpy slide off at speed. Each blade comes with a cleansing wipe which removes any dirt and film before your first use, and you're encouraged to run your wipers dry for a minute or two after using the cleaning up to build up some silicone on the windshield (optional, but recommended) -- after that it's totally automatic! We've been using these blades on our own BMWs for years, and would never go back to "traditional" wiper blades now.   Which side of my BMW is this wiper for?    Wiper blades are sold individually.

Each wiper insert is impregnated with a silicone agent, which automatically applies itself to the windshield as you wipe. The more you wipe, the better the "beading" effect of water droplets, causing droplets to simlpy slide off at speed. Each blade comes with a cleansing wipe which removes any dirt and film before your first use, and you're encouraged to run your wipers dry for a minute or two after using the cleaning up to build up some silicone on the windshield (optional, but recommended) -- after that it's totally automatic! We've been using these blades on our own BMWs for years, and would never go back to "traditional" wiper blades now.   Which side of my BMW is this wiper for?      Wiper blades are sold individually.

short-description: This is a high quality reproduction of the Euro-only model E46 M3 CSL style front bumper cover spoiler. Unlike the stock E46 M3 style bumper, this CSL style has no fog light openings, and a single duct on the driver's side that can be made to function as a cold air intake inlet/duct. The bumper is made of polypropylene (PP) plastic, just like a factory BMW bumper covers. It also features pre-installed carbon fiber lips, very much in keeping with the factory CSL part. Best of all, this CSL-inspired bumper is available for only a fraction of what a real CSL bumper would sell for -- the BMW dealers themselves are forbidden from ordering genuine CSL parts anymore, making the "real thing" even harder to come by. This bumper comes as shown, primed ready to prep and paint. Includes US license plate mount (bumper is pre-drilled to accpet the license plate mount). The screen for the intake hole is not included but can be added from the options below. Professional paint and installation is highly recommended.

...
short-description: This items is either referred to as the Hood Cowl Cover or Windshield Cowl Cover. It is the black plastic cover at the base of the windshield. Because the plastic is exposed to sunlight it becomes dry and cracks with age. And that can allow water down into the various compartments and cavities in the firewall where rust will form.   The Cowl Cover also fades which makes it stand out in an otherwise detailed engine bay. Replacing it will give your engine compartment a fresh and cared for appearance. The marginal cost of the part goes a long way in sprucing up the engine bay.   The MINI Cooper cowl cover appears to be one single piece but is actually a Left and Right. This part number covers the left side. Replacement is easy and straightforward but the wipers must be removed from the linkage. Remember to mark their position before removing.     2007+    MINI Cooper, MINI Cooper S  2007+    MINI Cooper Clubman, MINI Cooper S Clubman  2007+    MINI Cooper Convertible, MINI Cooper S Convertible,

cleanDesc: PIAA Super Silicone Wiper Blade - 18 inch - E53 X5 Rear
short-description: Made of silicone rubber, PIAA wiper blades ensure greater visibility by coating the windshield with silicone to promote continuous water beading in inclement weather. Water beads up into droplets at low speeds that are easily removed by ordinary wiping. And at higher speeds, wind pressure pushes the water off the windshield, often without even requiring wiper use.     Each wiper insert is impregnated with a silicone agent, which automatically applies itself to the windshield as you wipe. The more you wipe, the better the "beading" effect of water droplets, causing droplets to simlpy slide off at speed. Each blade comes with a cleansing wipe which removes any dirt and film before your first use, and you're encouraged to run your wipers dry for a minute or two after using the cleaning up to build up some silicone on the windshield (optional, but recommended) -- after that it's totally automatic! We've been using these blades on our own BMWs for years, and would never go back to "traditional" wiper blades now.     2000-2006    X5 3.0i X5 4.4i X5 4.6is X5 4.8is - Rear Wiper    Wiper blades are sold individually.

short-description: Fitting a front license plate to a BMW requires drilling damaging holes forever ruining the original front bumper. Until now, the only other option was to fit an offset mount to the side using the factory tow hook. Carbonio has now engineered an OEM quality solution that mounts the license plate in the middle while doing no damage of any kind. Installation and removal is a 10-second exercise and the unit is totally self-contained, not requiring any pieces to be fixed to the car. FEATURES NO-DRILL, NO-HOLES, NO-ADHESIVES OR TAPES Easy 10-second-on 10-second-off installation Fully tunable design allows for adjustment of license plate angle and distance forwards / backwards / upwards / downwards Allows for multiple plate mounting location options Great for car shows or track sessions when you want to quickly remove your front plate Soft material on contact surfaces protects grille Strong formed plate support accepts USA and Rest of World (ROW) license plates; a truly global solution Black powder coating offers clean OEM look and long-lasting finish High-speed tested & does not interfere with vehicle cooling, parking sensors, or front cameras Can be used with most license plate frames and clear/colored plate covers and protectors Meets all known international license plate display and mounting laws Unit is shipped pre-assembled with all hardware and is ready to mount out of the box KIT INCLUDES Pre-assembled license plate mount with adjustment tool Complete photographic installation instructions

cleanDesc: No Holes License Plate Bracket - E36, E90, E92, E82, Z3
short-description: Drill holes in your BMW's front bumper? No way! The 'NO HOLES' License Plate Bracket (NHLPB) allows you to mount a front plate to your BMW without having to drill into your front bumper. Instead, it utilizes a custom machined stud that screws into the towhook receptacle. All parts are made from Stainless Steel to ensure no rust. The mounting hardware utilizes nylock nuts or lock washers which will not loosen from vibration. The plate attachment screws are button head socket cap screws for a nice clean look. Comes complete with Tow Hook Bolt, Bracket, One-Piece Plate Holder, and Hardware Pack. Installation is quick and easy with standard hand tools. Note:      The Offset Bracket allows customers to move the backing plate 2 inches to the left or right as a work around for fog lights, parking sensors, or just a different look.

short-description: Founded in 2003 Seibon Carbon excels in delivering premium quality carbon fiber products to those with discerning tastes. Drivers such as Michele Abbate in her Scion FRS racecar, Fredric Aasbo in his Formula D Scion tC and even team RS-R in Asian Formula D all rely solely on Seibon to get them to the podium.

cleanDesc: F80 M3 Complete Exterior Trim Package
short-description: Looking for all of the F80 M3 exterior trim in one place? This package replaces the grilles and vents that come from the factory with tacky plastic chrome. We also replace the brightly colored front and rear reflectors with body colored inserts. Chrome is so '70s and seems like an afterthought on modern composite BMW bodywork. The matte and body-colored trim looks more serious and cohesive with the rest of the body. It shows that your M3 means business. Our complete trim package includes all of the M3 exterior accessories plus some optional items to further personalize your M3.

cleanDesc: Painted Key Hole Cover - F87 M2
short-description: It’s essential to pay attention to the little details when it comes to making sure your BMW looks as sleek as possible. This includes its key hole cover (key hole delete). These painted keyhole covers are a great way to achieve a clean and uniform look. No need to worry about fit, either; all the core parts are factory-original and BMW built. Each part is meticulously hand-sanded, primed, painted, and cleared, as well as polished using Rupes equipment. The icing on the cake? They’re each finished off with a coat of Adam’s paint sealant. The painted key hole cover is designed as a replacement insert for the original factory surround and lock cylinder. If your vehicle does not have an accessible lock cylinder on the trunk and you wish to gain access to the battery in the event of a power loss, we recommend installing the key hole cover on the original lock cylinder. By installing the cover on top of the lock cylinder it provides an emergency access point in the event the battery is drained. Tools required: Torx25 bit Small flat head screw driver or pick

short-description: Drill holes in your BMW i8's front bumper? No way! cleanDesc: PIAA Super Silicone Wiper Blade - 21 inch
short-description: Made of silicone rubber, PIAA wiper blades ensure greater visibility by coating the windshield with silicone to promote continuous water beading in inclement weather. Water beads up into droplets at low speeds that are easily removed by ordinary wiping. And at higher speeds, wind pressure pushes the water off the windshield, often without even requiring wiper use.     Each wiper insert is impregnated with a silicone agent, which automatically applies itself to the windshield as you wipe. The more you wipe, the better the "beading" effect of water droplets, causing droplets to simlpy slide off at speed. Each blade comes with a cleansing wipe which removes any dirt and film before your first use, and you're encouraged to run your wipers dry for a minute or two after using the cleaning up to build up some silicone on the windshield (optional, but recommended) -- after that it's totally automatic! We've been using these blades on our own BMWs for years, and would never go back to "traditional" wiper blades now.   Which side of my BMW is this wiper for?    Wiper blades are sold individually.

cleanDesc: Genuine BMW Windshield Cowl Cover - E36
short-description: This items is either referred to as the Hood Cowl Cover or Windshield Cowl Cover. It is the black plastic cover at the base of the windshield. There is a rubber seal that runs along the top edge that helps direct water down and away from the firewall. But because the rubber is exposed to sunlight it becomes dry and cracks with age. And that can allow water down into the various compartments and cavities in the firewall where rust will form.   The Cowl Cover also fades which makes it stand out in an otherwise detailed engine bay. Replacing it will give your engine compartment a fresh and cared for appearance. The marginal cost of the part goes a long way in sprucing up the engine bay. To finish off the restoration, add the "push button" mounting screws, new windshield wiper caps (wipers have to be removed to replace the Cowl Cover), and new clamps and grommets.   The E36 sedan cowl cover appears to be one single piece but is actually a Left and Right. This part number covers the right side. Replacement is easy and straightforward but the wipers must be removed from the linkage. Remember to mark their position before removing. It fits Sedan models only (not Coupes or Convertibles).     1992-1998    318i 318ti 325i 328i M3 - 4 Door Only

No Holes License Plate Bracket - E70 X5, E71 X6
short-description: Drill holes in your BMW's front bumper? No way! The 'NO HOLES' License Plate Bracket (NHLPB) allows you to mount a front plate to your BMW without having to drill into your front bumper. Instead, it utilizes a custom machined stud that screws into the towhook receptacle. All parts are made from Stainless Steel to ensure no rust. The mounting hardware utilizes nylock nuts or lock washers which will not loosen from vibration. The plate attachment screws are button head socket cap screws for a nice clean look. Comes complete with Tow Hook Bolt, Bracket, One-Piece Plate Holder, and Hardware Pack.. Installation is quick and easy with standard hand tools. Note:      The Offset Bracket allows customers to move the backing plate 2 inches to the left or right as a work around for fog lights, parking sensors, or just a different look.

short-description: Drill holes in your MINI's front bumper? No way! The 'NO HOLES' License Plate Bracket (NHLPB) allows you to mount a front plate to your BMW without having to drill into your front bumper. Instead, it utilizes a custom machined stud that screws into the towhook receptacle. All parts are made from Stainless Steel to ensure no rust. The mounting hardware utilizes nylock nuts or lock washers which will not loosen from vibration. The plate attachment screws are button head socket cap screws for a nice clean look. Comes complete with Tow Hook Bolt, Bracket, One-Piece Plate Holder, and Hardware Pack.. Installation is quick and easy with standard hand tools. Note:      The Offset Bracket allows customers to move the backing plate 2 inches to the left or right as a work around for fog lights, parking sensors, or just a different look.

No Holes License Plate Bracket - E89 Z4 2009+
short-description: Drill holes in your BMW's front bumper? No way! The 'NO HOLES' License Plate Bracket (NHLPB) allows you to mount a front plate to your BMW without having to drill into your front bumper. Instead, it utilizes a custom machined stud that screws into the towhook receptacle. All parts are made from Stainless Steel to ensure no rust. The mounting hardware utilizes nylock nuts or lock washers which will not loosen from vibration. The plate attachment screws are button head socket cap screws for a nice clean look. Comes complete with Tow Hook Bolt, Bracket, One-Piece Plate Holder, and Hardware Pack.. Installation is quick and easy with standard hand tools. Note:      The Offset Bracket allows customers to move the backing plate 2 inches to the left or right as a work around for fog lights, parking sensors, or just a different look.
